1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
This is Claude acting as an autonomous AI agent.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,500
I ask it for some compute — and to pay for it itself.

3
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:16,500
It calls request_compute and gets back an HTTP 402: payment required.

4
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:22,000
It decides to settle the payment on Casper.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Watch — it calls settle_on_casper and signs a real transaction.

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:38,000
Here's the deploy on the public Casper testnet explorer.

7
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Status: Success — and the PaymentSettled event, recorded on-chain.

8
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:50,500
Then the agent fetches the verified compute result.

9
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:58,000
AiFinPay is the x402 payment protocol; Casper is the settlement backend.

10
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:05,000
An AI agent just paid another agent — on-chain, by itself.
